 is used in every room of the house even in a bathroom.";i:31;s:71:"Using a chair rail is a good way to separate two materials on the wall.";i:32;s:73:"It is used usually to separate beadboards or subway tiles with the paint.";i:33;s:53:"Chair rails can be made of marble ceramic or plastic.";i:34;s:21:"Of course marble and.";i:35;s:121:"Chair rail height is a personal preference but theres something about a 36 inch height that looks a bit chinsy to my eye.";i:36;s:222:"A thirty six inch height also means the rail will be interrupted by the vanity so if you use a top molding thats thicker than the typical 34 backsplash you have to 45 it back or return it which again looks funny to my eye.";i:37;s:32:"Tile Chair Rail Height Bathroom.";i:38;s:250:"Tile Chair Rail Bathroom Traditional With Shower Tub Freestanding Basketweave Tile Design Ideas Tiling Floor Up To Chair Rail Height In Bathroom Hometalk Height Of Chair Rail That Runs Into Vanity READ Cleaning Panasonic Air Conditioner Outdoor Unit.";i:39;s:94:"The classic design feature is usually between 34 and 54 high with 36 being the average height.";i:40;s:44:"Most people dont immediately think of chair.";i:41;s:89:"In this case the room could easily accommodate a chair rail that is as high as 48 inches.";i:42;s:96:"The general rule of thumb is to position a chair rail in the lower one-third of the wall height.";i:43;s:161:"If you imagine the wall height divided vertically into three sections the chair rail is best placed at the line between the bottom and middle thirds of the wall.";i:44;s:40:"1920 craftsman style Victorian bathroom.";i:45;s:48:"Original chair rail and tall baseboard retained.";i:46;s:109:"Trim painted with Benjamin Moores Impervo oil paint color Glacial White chosen to best match the subway tile.";i:47;s:47:"The wall color is Behr UL230-20 Catalina Coast.";i:48;s:21:"Silver grey grout to.";i:49;s:110:"Here is the upstairs kids bathroom - floor tile and wall tile are different - wall is subway tile about 40 up.";i:50;s:62:"Next is main floor powder room - beadboard wallpaper wainscot.";i:51;s:60:"Last - Basement bathroom - subway tile wainscot about 40 up.";i:52;s:105:"If I could do it over - and I might I would possibly do the subway in the master too and a claw foot tub.";i:53;s:79:"There are no real rules to chair rails Ive installed them from 28 to 38 inches.";i:54;s:116:"Traditionally some feature like a window sill or a side board dictates the height so the lines flow around the room.";i:55;s:55:"But I always say beauty is in the eyes of the beholder.";i:56;s:171:"In the general sense a physical border like tile cap or chair rail between two building materials is usually aesthetic provided that the materials were installed properly.";i:57;s:128:"The one exception to this is in the case of a material with significant expansion potential with changes in climate namely wood.";i:58;s:61:"In that case a border can hide the necessary expansion joint.";}}